<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9;">
        <div style="background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px;">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <div style="display: inline-block; width: 60px; height: 60px; background: #e8f5e9; border-radius: 50%; line-height: 60px; font-size: 28px;">
                    &#10003;
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 style="color: #7A8F6E; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center;">Votre rendez-vous est confirmé !</h2>

            <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Bonjour {{ appointment.firstName }}, nous avons le plaisir de vous confirmer votre rendez-vous.
            </p>

            <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <h3 style="color: #7A8F6E; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;">Récapitulatif</h3>

                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <strong>Date :</strong> {{ appointment.desiredDate|date('d/m/Y') }}
                </div>

                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <strong>Heure :</strong> {{ appointment.desiredTime }}
                </div>

                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <strong>Service :</strong> {{ appointment.service }}
                </div>

                {% if appointment.organization %}
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <strong>Organisation :</strong> {{ appointment.organization }}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            {% if teams_link is defined and teams_link %}
            <div style="background: #e8f0fe; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #4B53BC; text-align: center;">
                <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <img src="https://img.icons8.com/color/48/microsoft-teams-2019.png" alt="Teams" width="36" height="36" style="vertical-align: middle;">
                </div>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #4B53BC;">Rejoignez la réunion Teams</p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.9em;">
                    Le {{ appointment.desiredDate|date('d/m/Y') }} à {{ appointment.desiredTime }} (durée : 1h)
                </p>
                <a href="{{ teams_link }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 35px; background: #4B53BC; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1em;">
                    Rejoindre la réunion
                </a>
                <p style="margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 0.8em; color: #888;">
                    Ou copiez ce lien : <a href="{{ teams_link }}" style="color: #4B53BC; word-break: break-all;">{{ teams_link }}</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 4px solid #f0a030;">
                <strong>Important :</strong> En cas d'empêchement, merci de nous prévenir au moins 24h à l'avance par téléphone au <strong>06 83 42 40 12</strong> ou par email à <strong>contact@harmonieetsens.fr</strong>.
            </div>

            <p style="color: #666; text-align: center;">
                Nous avons hâte de vous rencontrer !<br>
                <strong>L'équipe Harmonie & Sens</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
